|url=https://www.informationweek.com/desktop/vista-the-anti-linux/d/d-id/1042748?piddl_msgorder=thrd
|title=Vista: the 'Anti-Linux'?
|date=May 1, 2006}}&lt;/ref&gt;

Their stories are cited by major news sources&lt;ref name=TheRegister.NYT2012&gt;{{cite newspaper |newspaper=[[The New York Times]]
